                       Trance, Progressive House | Garuda

               320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 104 min | 240 Mb


Drive is the second studio album produced by Electronic dance music artist Gareth Emery. The album is the follow up to Gareth's first release - Northern Lights in 2010 The Album features vocals from Christina Novelli who also sung on Gareth's most successful single to date - Concrete Angel which has had over 17 million views on Youtube. Also featured are Gavin Beach, Ben Gold, LJ Ayrten, Asia Whiteacre, Krewella, Bo Bruce and Gareth's Sister Roxanne Emery
